{"ticker": "AUR", "company": "AURORA INNOVATION INC", "weight_sum": 1.65, "etfs": ["ARKQ"], "is_private": false, "query": "($AUR OR \"Aurora Innovation\") -is:retweet min_faves:10 since_time:1777935114 until_time:1777948829", "n_fetched": 5, "n_kept": 5, "n_dropped": 0, "kept": [{"type": "tweet", "id": "2051270556599672899", "url": "https://x.com/TheFoxRadar/status/2051270556599672899", "twitterUrl": "https://twitter.com/TheFoxRadar/status/2051270556599672899", "text": "$AUR \n\nHirschbach Motor Lines, one of the largest refrigerated carriers in the U.S., with ~3,000 power units, has just signed an MOU to scale its autonomous fleet with Aurora Driver up to 500 trucks.\n\nThat\u2019s the truly noteworthy part: this is not just another pilot. It\u2019s an experienced operator that, after accumulating +800,000 miles and more than 2,000 real loads with the system, decides to commit nearly 17% of its entire fleet to autonomy. In a segment as demanding as refrigerated (where any delay or temperature failure destroys the cargo), this decision is not taken lightly. It speaks to deep technical confidence and an ROI they are already seeing in operational efficiency and the ability to run 24/7.\n\nThis validates several key pillars of their strategy:\n\n\u2022 The Driver as a Service model works: they don\u2019t just sell hardware/software, they sell recurring autonomous miles.\n\n\u2022 Aurora\u2019s Level 4 technology is mature for high-volume routes (Fort Worth\u2013Phoenix, Laredo, etc.).\n\n\u2022 This opens the door for other carriers to follow Hirschbach\u2019s model if they don\u2019t want to be left behind; Aurora will enable margin expansion for those who adopt its technology. This moment will be explosive for $AUR.\n\nDeliveries starting in 2027. Recurring revenues in the hundreds of millions in the coming years. Real momentum in a segment where autonomy generates immediate and massive value: long-haul trucking.\n\nThis is not hype. It\u2019s serious commercial adoption by those who bear the most risk. Hirschbach is not betting on \u201cthe future.\u201d It\u2019s betting on $AUR because it\u2019s already working today.\n\nSource: https://t.co/qhvIgVmRwL", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "retweetCount": 2, "replyCount": 1, "likeCount": 23, "quoteCount": 0, "viewCount": 653, "createdAt": "Mon May 04 11:59:46 +0000 2026", "lang": "en", "bookmarkCount": 0, "isReply": false, "inReplyToId": null, "conversationId": "2051270556599672899", "displayTextRange": [0, 274], "inReplyToUserId": null, "inReplyToUsername": null, "author": {"type": "user", "userName": "TheFoxRadar", "url": "https://x.com/TheFoxRadar", "twitterUrl": "https://twitter.com/TheFoxRadar", "id": "2016491161033064448", "name": "The Fox Radar", "isVerified": false, "isBlueVerified": true, "verifiedType": null, "profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/2018818076867784704/SUo4OLsD_normal.jpg", "coverPicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_banners/2016491161033064448/1770236335", "description": "", "location": "Spain", "followers": 302, "following": 295, "status": "", "canDm": false, "canMediaTag": true, "createdAt": "Wed Jan 28 12:39:03 +0000 2026", "entities": {"description": {"urls": []}, "url": {}}, "fastFollowersCount": 0, "favouritesCount": 788, "hasCustomTimelines": true, "isTranslator": false, "mediaCount": 32, "statusesCount": 321, "withheldInCountries": [], "affiliatesHighlightedLabel": {}, "possiblySensitive": false, "pinnedTweetIds": ["2035376290979549413"], "profile_bio": {"description": "Early-stage picks for high long-term returns | Sharing my investments, macro insights & real opportunities   Not Financial Advice. $PRME $AUR $ASTS", "entities": {"description": {"symbols": [{"indices": [131, 136], "text": "PRME"}, {"indices": [137, 141], "text": "AUR"}, {"indices": [142, 147], "text": "ASTS"}]}}}, "isAutomated": false, "automatedBy": null}, "extendedEntities": {}, "card": {"binding_values": [{"key": "photo_image_full_size_large", "value": {"i